Welcome to the Ripple development container!

  Toolchain  : Clang/LLVM + ELD linker targeting all Hexagon versions
               supported by upstream LLVM (v81 is the latest)
  Test suite : /home/ripple/ripple-test-suite
  Docs       : /home/ripple/learn-ripple

For more information about the test suite:
  cat ripple-test-suite/README.md

Browse the documentation:
  mdbook serve --hostname 0.0.0.0 --port 3000 learn-ripple  (browser, needs -p <host-port>:3000 on docker run)

To run the test suite:
  cmake --build ripple-test-suite/build --target check

Tip: press Up or Ctrl+R to recall the commands above from history.
